fields.title: hello_user
fields.text:
Hello! I am a bot for watching feeds and sending new items to you.
Send:

/add_feed [url] to add new feed.
/list_feed to view all your feeds.
/delete_feed to delete feed.
/integrations to show what integrations I have.

fields.title: limit_achieved
fields.text:
You have achieved limit for feed.
Please contact to author to add more.

fields.title: integrations
fields.text:
Please send /authorize_pocket for activate Pocket integration.
Send /unauthorize_pocket for deactivate Pocket integration.

fields.title: url_not_founded
fields.text: Feed did not find. Please, retry.

fields.title: help
fields.text:
Send:

/add_feed [url] to add new feed.
/list_feed to view all your feeds.
/delete_feed to delete feed.
/integrations to show what integrations I have.
